WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:03.300
Your Majesty.

2
00:00:04.100 --> 00:00:05.600
I have something to report.

3
00:00:13.066 --> 00:00:15.400
Because Your Majesty stepped in with your right foot just now,

4
00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:16.700
I am not happy.

5
00:00:18.733 --> 00:00:20.000
If he stepped with the left foot,

6
00:00:20.066 --> 00:00:21.633
would he be unhappy too?

7
00:00:27.466 --> 00:00:29.433
What happened?

8
00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:33.500
Your Majesty, we have leads on the one we were pursuing.

9
00:00:33.533 --> 00:00:35.166
When we captured him,

10
00:00:35.166 --> 00:00:36.866
he bit down on a poison pill hidden in his mouth.

11
00:00:37.466 --> 00:00:38.866
He committed suicide with the poison.

12
00:00:45.133 --> 00:00:46.466
See where you can run now.

13
00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:49.066
Stop him!

14
00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:58.833
We were too late to save him.

15
00:00:58.900 --> 00:01:00.066
Please punish us, Your Majesty.

16
00:01:00.100 --> 00:01:01.200
How could this happen?

17
00:01:01.566 --> 00:01:02.766
But, but what?

18
00:01:02.766 --> 00:01:06.300
Quickly, say that the physician’s body has some oddities.

19
00:01:06.966 --> 00:01:08.800
As a physician,

20
00:01:08.933 --> 00:01:11.900
he should have been in contact with various medicines every day.

21
00:01:11.933 --> 00:01:13.366
Yet there is no trace of any medicine

22
00:01:13.366 --> 00:01:14.900
in the crevices of his nails.

23
00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.500
And the body has no medicinal smell at all.

24
00:01:17.666 --> 00:01:19.166
What do you mean?

25
00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:21.566
The physician was an imposter?

26
00:01:21.566 --> 00:01:24.700
I found after repeated examinations

27
00:01:25.266 --> 00:01:28.066
that this person’s face was covered with a human skin mask.

28
00:01:28.666 --> 00:01:30.066
In this case,

29
00:01:30.333 --> 00:01:31.700
Prince Duan is the puppet.

30
00:01:33.133 --> 00:01:33.933
I...

31
00:01:34.466 --> 00:01:37.200
The matter of the fake physician must not be leaked.

32
00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:40.066
I don't believe that person can vanish into thin air.

33
00:01:40.066 --> 00:01:43.000
You must investigate this discreetly.

34
00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:45.300
I will obey the order.

35
00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:50.366
Even if this physician were extraordinarily skilled,

36
00:01:50.366 --> 00:01:51.966
now that Prince Duan is dead,

37
00:01:51.966 --> 00:01:54.700
he cannot use anyone else to set up a stage.
